    "updated": "2026-07-07",
    "coordinate_note": "positions are normalized: nx = x/(width/2), nz = z/(depth/2), in [-1,1]; band radius r = max(|nx|,|nz|) (Chebyshev). Camera-near edge is +z (game camera_rig.gd offset (0,12,10)).",
    "gaps": [
      "density ranges are untested design-choices at the 3x scale; tune via game playtests, revise canon with provenance",
      "one asset kit exists (clockwork_observatory); non-HEARTH/BRASS regions reuse its shape taxonomy under region palettes until per-region kits ship",
      "entry-door far-arc check runs only when a room declares entry_door",
      "band model assumes rectangular floors"
    ]
  },
  "bands": {
    "combat_core": {"r_max": 0.55},
    "mid_band": {"r_min": 0.55, "r_max": 0.8},
    "perimeter_band": {"r_min": 0.8, "r_max": 1.0},
